        "height": 270,
        "content": "## Transaction-aware delivery\n\nOne strict AI call scores the full batch and only one destination branch runs. IDs are committed after that destination succeeds, so empty, duplicate, and failed-delivery runs remain safe.",
        "color": 7
      },
